<P>
   BBN-MADDUX _ ATLANTA _ Greg Maddux continues his late-season run
for the Cy Young. He goes for victory No. 20 on Thursday night in
New York, a mark he's reached only twice despite his numerous Cy
Young awards. (Stinson, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 20.
</P>
