Things Work'' can tell you, is a simple reciprocating pump that
operates on the principle of _ well, it would be a lot easier to
explain using one of the witty illustrations that fill Macaulay's
books and television programs. You could blow a gasket trying to
explain some of the principles that Macaulay, an author and
illustrator, distills into simple, illuminating images. By John
Leland.
