<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-27 19:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3995 &Cx1f; tab-z
u l BC-TRENDS-NEXTGEN-NYTSF     09-27 0959
