<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-27 19:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4000 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r l bc-DESIGN-HOOLYWOODHOUSE     09-27 1101
