<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-27 19:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4006 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r a bc-LADN-BUDGET     09-27 0169
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-LADN-BUDGET </SLUG>
bc-LADN-BUDGET 
<TEXT>
<P>
