<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-27 20:46 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4132 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a BC-CPT-WEB-BOGEYMAN-ART-     09-27 1425
</HEADER>
