imperial Russian art from the 18th and 19th centuries is the
greatest in the world outside Russia, and her estate has one of the
leading U.S. collections of Sevres porcelain, much of it
commissioned by Catherine the Great. View of the French Parterre
gardens from Post's bedroom window at the Hillwood Museum and
