<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-27 22:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4232 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s BC-FBC-WOLFCOL-COLUMN-LA     09-27 0828
